'''线粒体基质蛋白质'''（{{lang-en|mitochondrial matrix protein}}）是对存在于[[线粒体基质|线粒体基质]]中的[[蛋白质|蛋白质]]的统称。线粒体基质中蛋白质浓度较高，<ref>{{cite journal
 | author = Arthur Partikian, Bence Ölveczky, R. Swaminathan, Yuxin Li, and A.S. Verkman
 | title = Rapid diffusion of green fluorescent protein in the mitochondrial matrix 
 | journal = Journal of Cell Biology
 | volume = 140
 | issue = 4
 | pages = 821-829 
 | pmid = 
 | doi = 10.1083/jcb.140.4.821 
 | url = http://d.wanfangdata.com.cn/periodical_smdhx200504013.aspx
 | language = zh |date=Feb 23, 1998}}</ref>但其中只有极少数是由[[线粒体基因组|线粒体基因组]]内的[[基因|基因]]编码的，绝大多数是由[[核基因|核基因]]编码，经[[转录|转录]]并由[[细胞质基质|细胞质基质]]中的[[游离核糖体|游离核糖体]][[翻译_(遗传学)|翻译]]产生的。这些蛋白质包括[[DNA聚合酶|DNA聚合酶]]、[[RNA聚合酶|RNA聚合酶]]、[[柠檬酸合成酶|柠檬酸合成酶]]、[[乙醇脱氢酶|乙醇脱氢酶]]（[[酵母菌|酵母菌]]）、[[鸟氨酸氨基转移酶|鸟氨酸氨基转移酶]]（[[哺乳动物|哺乳动物]]）以及[[三羧酸循环酶系|三羧酸循环酶系]]中的[[酶|酶类]]等。在细胞质基质中合成的线粒体基质蛋白的转运过程较为复杂，它们需要在[[转运肽|转运肽]]及多种[[分子伴侣|分子伴侣]]的辅助下经[[主动运输|主动运输]]才能进入线粒体基质。线粒体基质蛋白不一定只在线粒体基质中[[基因表达|表达]]，它们也可以在线粒体外表达。<ref>{{cite journal
 | author = Jianzhong Jiang, Ying Zhang, Adrian R Krainer, Rui-Ming Xu
 | title = Crystal structure of human p32, a doughnut-shaped acidic mitochondrial matrix protein
 | journal = Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciencesofthe United States of America
 | volume = 96
 | issue = 7
 | pages = 3572-3577
 | pmid = 10097078
 | doi = 
 | url = http://www.pnas.org/content/96/7/3572.full.pdf 
 | language = en |date=Mar 30, 1999}}</ref>有猜测认为，这些存在于线粒体外的线粒体基质蛋白质是从线粒体中转运出去的，而此现象可能与线粒体起源于被[[真核细胞|真核细胞]][[胞吞|胞吞]]的[[原核细胞|原核细胞]]有关。<ref>{{cite journal
 |author      = Soltys BJ, Gupta RS
 |title       = Mitochondrial-matrix proteins at unexpected locations: are they exported?
 |journal     = Trends in Biochemical Sciences
 |volume      = 24
 |issue       = 5
 |pages       = 174-177
 |pmid        = 10322429
 |doi         = 10.1016/S0968-0004(99)01390-0
 |url         = http://www.science.mcmaster.ca/biochem/faculty/gupta/Reprints/mito11_TIBS1999.pdf
 |language    = en
 |date        = May 1999
 |deadurl     = yes
 |archiveurl  = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304063548/http://www.science.mcmaster.ca/biochem/faculty/gupta/Reprints/mito11_TIBS1999.pdf
 |archivedate = 2016-03-04
}}</ref>

